<p>Have you seen the movie <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0083866/?ref_=nv_sr_1">E.T.</a> or the Netflix series <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4574334/?ref_=nv_sr_1">Stranger Things</a>? Then you probably have some idea of what Role-Playing Games are. In this podcast I give a 20 minute introduction to RPGs in general and the <a href="http://d6gaming.org">Amar RPG</a> in particular. Get into the fun and excitement of adventure and creating stories together with your friends.</p>

